content: A new blog post is up! "How Much Do We (Plant Pathologists) Value Openness and Transparency?", @edelponte and @adamhsparks discuss their latest paper with @zacharyfoster et al. and what the implications are for plant pathology, why it may be so closed, and how we can be more open and reproducible in our research. #ReproducibleResearch #FAIRData #OpenResearch #OpenAccess

- Accessible : dans un entrepôt
- Interoperable : formats ouverts
- Reusable : licence ouverte
